comments: Lopez (MIL) extends his arm forward into Collins' (ATL) path and initiates contact that prevents Collins from disengaging following the pick.
Young (ATL) gathers the ball on his right foot, takes his first step on his left, and lands simultaneously on both feet for his second step.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) extends his arms into Collins' (ATL) upper body, and initiates contact that drives Collins off of his legally obtained rebounding position.
Carter (MIL) moves into and under Young's (ATL) body while he is airborne, and dislodges him as he pursues the rebound.
Holiday (MIL) is moving alongside Young's (ATL) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the same spot in transition.
Holiday (MIL) legally contests Young's (ATL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hunter (ATL) cleanly deflects the ball away from Lopez (MIL) during rebounding.  Any ensuing arm contact after the deflection is considered incidental.
Capela (ATL) is already in Hill's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs as Capela slightly re-establishes himself.
Capela (ATL) places his hand momentarily on Antetokounmpo's (MIL) side before immediately removing his hand.
Capela (ATL) legally contests Antetokounmpo's (MIL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Young (ATL) is bracing for the contact from Holiday (MIL) and marginal contact occurs as Young releases away from the contact.
Capela (ATL) fully clears the lane within three seconds, and is in the paint for less than three seconds when he begins to actively guard an opponent.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is already in Murray's (ATL) path and he absorbs the contact as he firms up over his right leg.
Murray (ATL) legally contests Holiday's (MIL) driving shot attempt.

Hunter (ATL) extends his arms into Matthews' (MIL) upper body, delivering contact that affects Matthews' FOM.  Additionally, this contact occurs prior to, and causes, the ensuing Matthews-Young (ATL) contact.
Murray (ATL) commits a take foul on Holiday (MIL).
Hunter (ATL) and Lopez (MIL) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Collins (ATL) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL).
Holiday (MIL) cleanly steals the ball from Young (ATL).
Capela (ATL) legally contests Antetokounmpo's (MIL) shot near the rim.
